  ('optometrist-moex-00710', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-112-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關眼的色像差（chromaticaberration）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["波長400nm和700nm在人眼的縱向（longitudinaloraxial）色像差約2D", "橫向（lateralortransverse）色像差比縱向色像差更會影響視力", "超過±8.00D鏡片才會造成橫向色像差", "人眼會適應色像差"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:43+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "77d308980065", "answer_pdf_sha1": "815ebca9fd63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
